Package: FOSBAAS
Type: Package
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-06-29
Title: Functions and Data for Fundamentals of Sports Business Analytics and Strategy
Authors@R: c(person("Justin", "Watkins", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "watkinsjudo@gmail.com"))
Author: Justin Watkins [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Justin Watkins <watkinsjudo@gmail.com>
Description: A companion package for the book "Fundamentals of Sports Business
    Analytics and Strategy" (FOSBAAS). It bundles the example data sets used
    throughout the book together with the simulation and helper functions that
    generated them. The data describe a fictional professional sports franchise
    (tickets, customers, demographics, promotions, secondary-market sales and
    ballpark operations) and let readers reproduce the analyses end to end. The
    simulation functions are intentionally simple and are meant for teaching
    rather than production use.
